  "identifier": "HB 318",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to property rights in name, voice, and likeness.",
  "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 365 to define terms; establish property rights in every individual's name, voice, and likeness; establish how the property rights may be transferred or terminated; establish a civil cause of action and damages for unauthorized use of an individual's name, voice, or likeness; provide exceptions; require that an action commence within 4 years of discovery of the violation.",
